		<div class="container-fluid" style="margin-top:-10px;">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-xs-6 text-center">
					<a href="#" onclick="openSettings('sensors');">
						<h3><span class="fa fa-2x fa-bullseye"></span></h3>
						<p>Sensors settings</p>
					</a>
					<!-- </div> -->
					<p class="hidden-xs">
						<i>In <b>Sensors settings</b> one can find details for the sensors used, enable or disable them, set the default sensor or change their name and location.</i>
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-xs-6 text-center">
					<a href="#" onclick="openSettings('database');">
						<h3><span class="fa fa-2x fa-database"></span></h3>
						<p>Database functions</p>
					</a>
					<p class="hidden-xs" >
						<i>In <b>Database functions</b> the user can archive the temperarure data stored and can also export temperature data for the whole time in a comma seperated values .csv file that can later be viewed with a spreadsheet application.</i>
					</p>					
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row hidden-xs" style="margin-top:40px;">
			</div>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-xs-6 text-center">
					<a href="#" onclick="openSettings('account');">
						<h3><span class="fa fa-2x fa-user"></span></h3>
						<p>Login account</p>
					</a>
					<p class="hidden-xs">
						<i>In <b>Login account</b> the user can change the name and password used to enter <b>Pyre</b>. This can only be done if the user is authenticated!</i>
					</p>	
				</div>
				<div class="col-xs-6 text-center">
					<a href="#" onclick="openSettings('system');">
						<h3><span class="fa fa-2x fa-sliders"></span></h3>
						<p>System</p>
					</a>
					<p class="hidden-xs">
						<i>In <b>System</b> the user can adjust various thermostat's settings and modules regarding various functionalities (mqtt sensors, xbee sensors, amazon alexa support, ...) </b>.</i>
					</p>	
				</div>				
			</div>
		</div>

</body>

<% include ../partials/javascript.ejs %>
<script src="/javascripts/custom.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript">
	function openSettings(page){
		if (page==='sensors'){
			var name='backUrl';
			var setUrl = "http://<%=base_url%>/config/sensors";
		}
		else if (page==='database'){
			var name='backUrl';
			var setUrl = "http://<%=base_url%>/config/database";
		}
		else if (page==='account'){
			var name='backUrl';
			var setUrl = "http://<%=base_url%>/config/account";
		}
		else if (page==='timewindows'){
			var name='backUrl_edit';
			var setUrl = "http://<%=base_url%>/config/timewindows";
		}
		else if (page==='system'){
			var name='backUrl';
			var setUrl = "http://<%=base_url%>/config/system";
		}
		else if (page==='about'){
			var name='backUrl';
			var setUrl = "http://<%=base_url%>/about";
		}		
		createCookie(name, window.location.href);
		window.location.href = setUrl;
	}
</script>